家因随机机制和游戏理解而产生的变数会很多，这也是我们希望看到的。","short_description":"这是一款东方幻想风格的回合制战棋策略游戏，在传统回合制战棋游戏的基础上，融入了更合理的成长模式，个例性更强的角色机制，更深的策略上限，以及丰富的收集成长要素。roguelike类系统机制会让意外感伴随你每步操作，在独特的东方韵味剧情中经历这趟抉择与成长的有趣旅程。","fullgame":{"appid":"1525410","name":"Wulin Chess"},"supported_languages":"Simplified Chinese<strong>*<\/strong>, English<br><strong>*<\/strong>languages with full audio support","header_image":"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1662240\/header.jpg?t=1639103071","website":null,"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:<\/strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:<\/strong> Windows 7 or later<br><\/li><li><strong>Processor:<\/strong> i5-3570 3.4 GHz 4 Core<br><\/li><li><strong>Memory:<\/strong> 4 GB RAM<br><\/li><li><strong>DirectX:<\/strong> Version 10<br><\/li><li><strong>Storage:<\/strong> 2048 MB available space<\/li><\/ul>"},"mac_requirements":[],"linux_requirements":[],"developers":["青岛三脚猫工作室"],"publishers":["青岛三脚猫工作室"],"package_groups":[],"platforms":{"windows":true,"mac":false,"linux":false},"categories":[{"id":2,"description":"Single-player"},{"id":10,"description":"Game demo"}],"screenshots":[{"id":0,"path_thumbnail":"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1662240\/ss_425277184be4d33130f1be668c96bd6803627856.600x338.jpg?t=1639103071","path_full":"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1662240\/ss_425277184be4d33130f1be668c96bd6803627856.1920x1080.jpg?t=1639103071"},{"id":1,"path_thumbnail":"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1662240\/ss_1efdb09a708d89769f9fb04ea7e0c75eb5880627.600x338.jpg?t=1639103071","path_full":"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1662240\/ss_1efdb09a708d89769f9fb04ea7e0c75eb5880627.1920x1080.jpg?t=1639103071"},{"id":2,"path_thumbnail":"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1662240\/ss_ae4e5a43ac71650ec38891ca6f1fd61d640acb1f.600x338.jpg?t=1639103071","path_full":"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1662240\/ss_ae4e5a43ac71650ec38891ca6f1fd61d640